data.description: Country Living at its Finest!!! Welcome home to this freshly updated 4 bedroom Tri-level on just under an ACRE. As you pull in the long driveway with turnaround, you'll notice the freshly painted exterior(April 2024). Hop out and envision your chickens welcoming you home.(Chicken coup out back). Open that door and you'll notice that it's brand new also!! Enjoy main level living with the living room, Dining and kitchen all receiving Luxury vinyl floors. Cruise through the kitchen and see those new 2022 appliances that are included. Yep, that's a half bath by the garage you saw!! Did I mention the oversized 2 car garage? It's there for all your stuff! Moving up the stairs,you can feel comfortable sleeping knowing the HVAC was recently updated to Forced Air for those warm summer nights. Did I mention it was connected to Natural gas as well! Going down the stairs you'll catch the 4th bedroom and additional living space to get that big comfy sectional in. New lower level wallside windows are already ordered. (May 2024) Heading into the backyard, you'll love the large shed that will store all those extra things and maybe a chicken or two!!! Cluck, Cluck. Don't miss out on the chance to homestead on a budget.
